@BFF.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5000

### Health Check
GET {{BFF.API_HostAddress}}/health

### Health Check Detalhado
GET {{BFF.API_HostAddress}}/api/health

### Status da API
GET {{BFF.API_HostAddress}}/api/health/status

### Swagger OpenAPI
GET {{BFF.API_HostAddress}}/swagger/v1/swagger.json

### Swagger UI
GET {{BFF.API_HostAddress}}/swagger

### ===== AUTENTICAÇÃO =====

### Registrar novo usuário (Aluno)
POST {{BFF.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "aluno@teste.com",
  "password": "MinhaSenh@123",
  "nome": "João Silva",
  "dataNascimento": "1995-05-15T00:00:00",
  "ehAdministrador": false
}

### Registrar novo usuário (Admin)
POST {{BFF.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@teste.com",
  "password": "MinhaSenh@123",
  "nome": "Admin Sistema",
  "dataNascimento": "1990-01-01T00:00:00",
  "ehAdministrador": true
}

### Login
POST {{BFF.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "aluno@teste.com",
  "password": "MinhaSenh@123"
}

### Refresh Token
POST {{BFF.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "seu_refresh_token_aqui"
}

### ===== ALUNOS =====

### Obter meu perfil (Requer JWT de Aluno)
GET {{BFF.API_HostAddress}}/api/alunos/meu-perfil
Authorization: Bearer {token}

### Atualizar meu perfil (Requer JWT de Aluno)
PUT {{BFF.API_HostAddress}}/api/alunos/meu-perfil
Authorization: Bearer {token}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "telefone": "(11) 99999-9999",
  "genero": "Masculino",
  "cidade": "São Paulo",
  "estado": "SP",
  "cep": "01234-567"
}

### Obter minhas matrículas (Requer JWT de Aluno)
GET {{BFF.API_HostAddress}}/api/alunos/minhas-matriculas
Authorization: Bearer {token}

### ===== DASHBOARD =====

### Dashboard do Aluno (Requer JWT)
GET {{BFF.API_HostAddress}}/api/dashboard/aluno
Authorization: Bearer {token}

### Dashboard do Admin (Requer JWT)
GET {{BFF.API_HostAddress}}/api/dashboard/admin
Authorization: Bearer {token}
